`MEMORY.md` was not present anywhere in this worktree, so that AGENTS prerequisite could not be followed literally.

I based the TDD/process read on the required output artifact at [0.6.1-WF-FIX-1-axis-e-idempotent-publish-output.json](/tmp/fdb-0.6.1-WF-FIX-1-axis-e-idempotent-publish-20260525T010638Z/dev/plans/runs/0.6.1-WF-FIX-1-axis-e-idempotent-publish-output.json:19). It describes a plausible genuine RED, but with only one implementer commit on the branch, the “test written first” sequencing is not independently provable from git history alone.

I did not execute the helper test in this read-only sandbox. The verdict is from diff and file inspection.
